        "action": "Ban after school detentions and isolation punishments in school",
        "additional_details": "Its wrong to give half an hour detention for being q minute late.\r\nThese children are people not objects and shouldn't in my opinion and others be made to sit in what children call a box and stare at a wall for what could be up to 1.5 hours at a time and pupils cannot turnaround even.",
        "background": "Stop detentions after school..children are put at risk when walking home alone and sometimes in the dark.. it isn't acceptable in my opinion.\r\nAlso stop isolation punishment..look at other options..we had to write lines",
